The Pastor Who Becomes a Vigilante | The Masked Saint | HD Action Drama Movie - Inspired by true events. Professional wrestler Chris Samuels retires from the ring and settles down as a pastor by day. By night, he confronts injustice as a masked vigilante.

Watch The Masked Saint, an action-packed drama inspired by true events. After retiring from professional wrestling, Chris Samuels begins a new life as a pastor, hoping to bring peace and guidance to his community. But when he sees the injustice around him, he secretly returns to the fight, this time as a masked vigilante determined to protect the vulnerable. Perfect for fans of inspirational action movies, full free drama films, vigilante hero stories, faith-based action movies, and real-life inspired thrillers, The Masked Saint delivers heart, redemption, and powerful heroism both inside and outside the ring.
